# Biome Linting

**Always check Biome linting** when editing code in this repo.

- After making edits, run `pnpm exec biome check .` (or `pnpm run lint`) to ensure no new lint or format issues.
- Fix any Biome errors or warnings before considering the task done.
- The project uses Biome for formatting and linting; keep changes consistent with `biome.json`.
